            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and the <strong>sultanas</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>sultana rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
