    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
